The pronounciation of the word वषट् , may optionally be by raising the voice (accutely accented), or it may be pronounced with monotony.<br><br>Terms: एकश्रुति

१.२.३६|विभाषा छन्दसि|विभाषा छन्दसि १.२.३६|१.२.३६ विभाषा छन्दसि
