३.२.१८५|पुवः संज्ञायाम्|पुवः संज्ञायाम् ३.२.१८५|३.२.१८५ पुवः संज्ञायाम्
The affix इत्र comes after the verb पू 'to purify' with the sense of the agent so expressed being the instrument when the sense of the complete word is simply appellative and not descriptive.<br><br>Terms: इत्र

३.२.१८६|कर्तरि चर्षिदेवतयोः|कर्तरि चर्षिदेवतयोः ३.२.१८६|३.२.१८६ कर्तरि चर्षिदेवतयोः
The affix इत्र comes after the verb पू 'to purify' with the sense of the agent or instrument when it is respectively used in connection with a sage or a deity.<br><br>Terms: इत्र

३.२.१८७|ञीतः क्तः|ञीतः क्तः ३.२.१८७|३.२.१८७ ञीतः क्तः
The verbal roots marked with an indicatory ञि , take the affix क्त , in denoting the present time.<br><br>Terms: क्त

३.२.१८८|मतिबुद्धिपूजार्थेभ्यश्च|मतिबुद्धिपूजार्थेभ्यश्च ३.२.१८८|३.२.१८८ मतिबुद्धिपूजार्थेभ्यश्च
And after the roots denoting inclination, understanding, or respect, the affix क्त is used with the force of the present<br><br>Terms: क्त

३.३.१|उणादयो बहुलम्|उणादयो बहुलम् ३.३.१|३.३.१ उणादयो बहुलम्
The affixes उण् and the rest with the force of the present and with a sense simply appellative are attached diversely.<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.२|भूतेऽपि दृश्यन्ते|भूतेऽपि दृश्यन्ते ३.३.२|३.३.२ भूतेऽपि दृश्यन्ते
The उणादि affixes are seen also attached with the force of the past time.<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.३|भविष्यति गम्यादयः|भविष्यति गम्यादयः ३.३.३|३.३.३ भविष्यति गम्यादयः
The words गामि etc. are valid forms having the sense of the future time.<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.४|यावत्पुरानिपातयोर्लट्|यावत्पुरानिपातयोर्लट् ३.३.४|३.३.४ यावत्पुरानिपातयोर्लट्
The affix लट् (Present Tense) comes after a root with the force of futurity when it has in construction with it the particles यावत् and पुरा।<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.५|विभाषा कदाकर्ह्योः|विभाषा कदाकर्ह्योः ३.३.५|३.३.५ विभाषा कदाकर्ह्योः
The affix लट् (Present Tense) is optionally used after a root with the force of the futurity when it has in construction with it the adverbs कदा and कर्हि।<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.६|किंवृत्ते लिप्सायाम्|किंवृत्ते लिप्सायाम् ३.३.६|३.३.६ किंवृत्ते लिप्सायाम्
When the word किम् or its derivatives are in construction with a verb, the affix लट् (Present Tense) is used optionally after a root, in denoting future time, provided that the sentences expresses a desire of gaining on the part of the speaker.<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.७|लिप्स्यमानसिद्धौ च|लिप्स्यमानसिद्धौ च ३.३.७|३.३.७ लिप्स्यमानसिद्धौ च
And when the success, that would accrue to another by fulfilling the desire of the speaker, is indicated in a sentence, the present tense may optionally be used with the force of the futurity.<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.८|लोडर्थलक्षणे च|लोडर्थलक्षणे च ३.३.८|३.३.८ लोडर्थलक्षणे च
The affix लट् (Present Tense) is optionally used with the force of futurity after that root, which is in a conditional sentence, is the condition precedent for the action indicated by another verb having the sense of the imperative mood.<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.९|लिङ् चोर्ध्वमौहूर्तिके|लिङ् चोर्ध्वमौहूर्तिके ३.३.९|३.३.९ लिङ् चोर्ध्वमौहूर्तिके
The लट् (Present Tense) or the लिङ् (Potential) is used under similar conditions in denoting futurity, when the future time is future by a मूहूर्त (= 48 minutes).<br><br>Terms: उणादि

३.३.१०|तुमुन्ण्वुलौ क्रियायां क्रियार्थायाम्‌|तुमुन्ण्वुलौ क्रियायां क्रियार्थायाम्‌ ३.३.१०|३.३.१० तुमुन्ण्वुलौ क्रियायां क्रियार्थायाम्‌
The affixes तुमुन् and ण्वुल् are placed after a verbal root with the force of the future when the word in construction therewith is another verb, denoting an action performed for the sake of the (future) action.<br><br>Terms: तुमुन् and ण्वुल्

३.३.११|भाववचनाश्च|भाववचनाश्च ३.३.११|३.३.११ भाववचनाश्च
And the affixes that are ordained to come after a root with the force of denoting the mere action of the verb, such as धञ् etc. -- लोहितादिडाज्भ्यः क्यष् ३.१.३, have also the force of the future, when the word in construction therewith is another verb denoting an action performed for the sake of the future action.<br><br>Terms: धञ्

३.३.१२|अण् कर्मणि च|अण् कर्मणि च ३.३.१२|३.३.१२ अण् कर्मणि च
The affix अण् comes after a root with the force of the future when the word in construction with it is in the Accusative -2nd case and when the action is performed for the sake of another action.<br><br>Terms: अण्

३.३.१३|लृट् शेषे च|लृट् शेषे च ३.३.१३|३.३.१३ लृट् शेषे च
The affix लृट् (2nd Future) is used after a verb in the remaining cases where futurity pure and simple is indicated and also where there is construction with it another verb denoting an action performed for the sake of the future action.<br><br>Terms: लृट्

३.३.१४|लृटः सद् वा|लृटः सद् वा ३.३.१४|३.३.१४ लृटः सद् वा
The affixes called सत् i.e. शतृ and शानच् are optionally the substitutes of लृट् (2nd Future).<br><br>Terms: लृट्

३.३.१५|अनद्यतने लुट्|अनद्यतने लुट् ३.३.१५|३.३.१५ अनद्यतने लुट्
The affix लुट् (1st Future) comes after a verbal root in the sense of what will happen but not in the course of the current day.<br><br>Terms: लुट्

३.३.१६|पदरुजविशस्पृशो घञ्|पदरुजविशस्पृशो घञ् ३.३.१६|३.३.१६ पदरुजविशस्पृशो घञ्
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. पद् 'to pace' 2. रुज् 'to pain 3. विश् 'to enter' 4. स्पृश् 'to touch'.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.१७|सृ स्थिरे|सृ स्थिरे ३.३.१७|३.३.१७ सृ स्थिरे
The affix घञ् comes after the verb शृ 'to move' when the agent is permanently fixed.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.१८|भावे|भावे ३.३.१८|३.३.१८ भावे
The affix घञ् comes after a root when mere action is denoted.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.१९|अकर्तरि च कारके संज्ञायाम्|अकर्तरि च कारके संज्ञायाम् ३.३.१९|३.३.१९ अकर्तरि च कारके संज्ञायाम्
The affix घञ् comes after a root when the sense is that of an appellative, the word being related to the verb from which its name is deduced, but not as agent.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२०|परिमाणाख्यायां सर्वेभ्यः|परिमाणाख्यायां सर्वेभ्यः ३.३.२०|३.३.२० परिमाणाख्यायां सर्वेभ्यः
The affix घञ् comes after all roots when the word so formed is the name of a measure.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२१|इङश्च|इङश्च ३.३.२१|३.३.२१ इङश्च
The affix घञ् comes after the root इङ् 'to study'.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२२|उपसर्गे रुवः|उपसर्गे रुवः ३.३.२२|३.३.२२ उपसर्गे रुवः
The affix घञ् comes after the verb रू 'to roar' when it has an उपसर्ग in composition with it.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२३|समि युद्रुदुवः|समि युद्रुदुवः ३.३.२३|३.३.२३ समि युद्रुदुवः
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. यु 'to join' 2. द्रु 'to run' 3. दु 'to burn' when in composition with the preposition सम्।<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२४|श्रिणीभुवोऽनुपसर्गे|श्रिणीभुवोऽनुपसर्गे ३.३.२४|३.३.२४ श्रिणीभुवोऽनुपसर्गे
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. शृ 'to go to' 2. नी 'to lead' 3. भू 'to be' when not in composition with an उपसर्ग ।<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२५|वौ क्षुश्रुवः|वौ क्षुश्रुवः ३.३.२५|३.३.२५ वौ क्षुश्रुवः
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. क्षु 'to sneeze' 2. श्रु 'to move and hear' when the preposition वि is in composition.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२६|अवोदोर्नियः|अवोदोर्नियः ३.३.२६|३.३.२६ अवोदोर्नियः
The affix घञ् comes after the verb नी 'to lead' when the prepositions अव and उत् are in composition.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२७|प्रे द्रुस्तुस्रुवः|प्रे द्रुस्तुस्रुवः ३.३.२७|३.३.२७ प्रे द्रुस्तुस्रुवः
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. द्रु 'to run' 2. स्तु 'to praise' 3. श्रु 'to move and hear' when the word in composition is प्र।<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२८|निरभ्योः पूल्वोः|निरभ्योः पूल्वोः ३.३.२८|३.३.२८ निरभ्योः पूल्वोः
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. पू 'to purify' 2. लू 'to cut' when निर् and अभि are respectively in composition.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.२९|उन्न्योर्ग्रः|उन्न्योर्ग्रः ३.३.२९|३.३.२९ उन्न्योर्ग्रः
The affix घञ् comes after the root गॄ when the उपसर्ग-s उत् and नि are in composition.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३०|कॄ धान्ये|कॄ धान्ये ३.३.३०|३.३.३० कॄ धान्ये
The affix घञ् comes after the verb कॄ when the prepositions उत् and नि are in composition and when the sense of the verb relates to grain.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३१|यज्ञे समि स्तुवः|यज्ञे समि स्तुवः ३.३.३१|३.३.३१ यज्ञे समि स्तुवः
The affix घञ् comes after the verb स्तु 'to praise' when it is preceded by the उपसर्ग सम् and the word refers to sacrificial subjects.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३२|प्रे स्त्रोऽयज्ञे|प्रे स्त्रोऽयज्ञे ३.३.३२|३.३.३२ प्रे स्त्रोऽयज्ञे
The affix घञ् comes after the verb स्तॄ 'to cover' when preceded by the preposition प्र ; provided that the word so formed does not refer to sacrifice.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३३|प्रथने वावशब्दे|प्रथने वावशब्दे ३.३.३३|३.३.३३ प्रथने वावशब्दे
The affix घञ् comes after the verb स्तॄ 'to cover' when the preposition वि is in composition with it when the sense is that of extension and when such spreading does not refer to words.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३४|छन्दोनाम्नि च|छन्दोनाम्नि च ३.३.३४|३.३.३४ छन्दोनाम्नि च
The affix घञ् comes after the verb स्तॄ 'to cover' with the उपसर्ग वि when the word so formed is the name of a metre.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३५|उदि ग्रहः|उदि ग्रहः ३.३.३५|३.३.३५ उदि ग्रहः
The affix घञ् comes after the verb ग्रह् 'to seize' when the preposition उत् is in composition.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३६|समि मुष्टौ|समि मुष्टौ ३.३.३६|३.३.३६ समि मुष्टौ
The affix घञ् comes after the verb ग्रह् 'to seize' when in composition with preposition सम् when the sense of the root refers to fist.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३७|परिन्योर्नीणोर्द्यूताभ्रेषयोः|परिन्योर्नीणोर्द्यूताभ्रेषयोः ३.३.३७|३.३.३७ परिन्योर्नीणोर्द्यूताभ्रेषयोः
The affix घञ् comes after the roots 1. नी 'to lead' 2. इ 'to go' when the prepositions परि and नि respectively in composition with them and when the words so formed respectively mean 'a game' and 'propriety or arrangement or law'.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३८|परावनुपात्यय इणः|परावनुपात्यय इणः ३.३.३८|३.३.३८ परावनुपात्यय इणः
The affix घञ् comes after the root इ 'to go' in composition with the word परि when the sense is that of following in regular succession.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.३९|व्युपयोः शेतेः पर्याये|व्युपयोः शेतेः पर्याये ३.३.३९|३.३.३९ व्युपयोः शेतेः पर्याये
The affix घञ् comes after the root सी 'to lie down' when the prepositions वि and उप are in composition with it and when the sense of the word so formed is that of 'regular succession'.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४०|हस्तादाने चेरस्तेये|हस्तादाने चेरस्तेये ३.३.४०|३.३.४० हस्तादाने चेरस्तेये
The affix घञ् comes after the root चि 'to collect' when the sense expressed is that of taking by hand provided it does not refer to stealing.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४१|निवासचितिशरीरोपसमाधानेष्वादेश्च कः|निवासचितिशरीरोपसमाधानेष्वादेश्च कः ३.३.४१|३.३.४१ निवासचितिशरीरोपसमाधानेष्वादेश्च कः
The affix घञ् comes after the roots चि 'to collect' and क is the substitute of the initial च in these senses viz. - 1. 'a dwelling' 2. 'a fire on the funeral pile' 3. 'the body' 4. 'collection'.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४२|संघे चानौत्तराधर्ये|संघे चानौत्तराधर्ये ३.३.४२|३.३.४२ संघे चानौत्तराधर्ये
The affix घञ् comes after the roots चि 'to collect' and क is the substitute of the initial च in the sense of 'a multitude or assembly' (of living beings possessing some common characteristics) but not merely a confused crowd of men.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४३|कर्मव्यतिहारे णच् स्त्रियाम्|कर्मव्यतिहारे णच् स्त्रियाम् ३.३.४३|३.३.४३ कर्मव्यतिहारे णच् स्त्रियाम्
The affix णच् comes after a root in denoting reciprocity of action and the word so formed is in the feminine gender.<br><br>Terms: णच्

३.३.४४|अभिविधौ भाव इनुण्|अभिविधौ भाव इनुण् ३.३.४४|३.३.४४ अभिविधौ भाव इनुण्
The affix इनुण् comes after a root in denoting condition when co-extensiveness is meant.<br><br>Terms: इनुण्

३.३.४५|आक्रोशेऽवन्योर्ग्रहः|आक्रोशेऽवन्योर्ग्रहः ३.३.४५|३.३.४५ आक्रोशेऽवन्योर्ग्रहः
The affix घञ् comes after the root ग्रह् 'to seize' in composition with अव and नि when maledicition is meant.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४६|प्रे लिप्सायाम्|प्रे लिप्सायाम् ३.३.४६|३.३.४६ प्रे लिप्सायाम्
The affix घञ् comes after the root ग्रह् 'to seize' when the word प्र is in composition and the sense denoted is the desire of acquisition.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४७|परौ यज्ञे|परौ यज्ञे ३.३.४७|३.३.४७ परौ यज्ञे
The affix घञ् comes after the root ग्रह् 'to seize' in composition with परि when it relates to sacrificial subjects.<br><br>Terms: घञ्

३.३.४८|नौ वृ धान्ये|नौ वृ धान्ये ३.३.४८|३.३.४८ नौ वृ धान्ये
