A stem (formed by an affix or an augment or substitute) having an indicatory च् gets acute on the end syllable.<br><br>Terms: accent

६.१.१६४|तद्धितस्य|तद्धितस्य ६.१.१६४|६.१.१६४ तद्धितस्य
