A stem formed by a तद्धित-affix having an indicatory क , has acute accent on the end syllable.<br><br>Terms: accent-तद्धित

६.१.१६६|तिसृभ्यो जसः|तिसृभ्यो जसः ६.१.१६६|६.१.१६६ तिसृभ्यो जसः
The Nominative Plural (जस्) of तिस् has acute accent on the last syllable.<br><br>Terms: accent-तद्धित

