The acute accent falls on the first syllable of the reduplicate verbs when followed by an affix beginning with a vowel (the vowel being not नुट्) and being a सार्वधातुक Personal-ending.<br><br>Terms: accent-तिङ्

६.१.१९०|अनुदात्ते च|अनुदात्ते च ६.१.१९०|६.१.१९० अनुदात्ते च
