The Names ending in अवति have the acute accent on the last syllable.<br><br>Terms: accent-word-Feminine

६.१.२२१|ईवत्याः|ईवत्याः ६.१.२२१|६.१.२२१ ईवत्याः
The Names ending in ईवति have the acute on the last syllable.<br><br>Terms: accent-तिङ्

