The augment इट् is not added to that affix which is joined to a root which is joined to a root, which in the Grammatical system of Instruction (i.e. in the धातुपाठ) is one syllable and is without accent (अनुदात्त).<br><br>Terms: इट् augment

७.२.११|श्र्युकः किति|श्र्युकः किति ७.२.११|७.२.११ श्र्युकः किति
