७.४.८२|गुणो यङ्लुकोः|गुणो यङ्लुकोः ७.४.८२|७.४.८२ गुणो यङ्लुकोः
गुण is substituted for the final of इ and उ (with their long) of a reduplicate when the Intensive character यङ् follows and also when it is elided.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८३|दीर्घोऽकितः|दीर्घोऽकितः ७.४.८३|७.४.८३ दीर्घोऽकितः
A long vowel is substituted for the अ of the reduplicate in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्) when the reduplicate receives no augment having an indicatory क् ।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८४|नीग्वञ्चुस्रंसुध्वंसुभ्रंसुकसपतपदस्कन्दाम्|नीग्वञ्चुस्रंसुध्वंसुभ्रंसुकसपतपदस्कन्दाम् ७.४.८४|७.४.८४ नीग्वञ्चुस्रंसुध्वंसुभ्रंसुकसपतपदस्कन्दाम्
The augment नीक् is added to the reduplicate of the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्) in the following - 1. वञ्च् 2. संस्र 3. ध्वंस् 3. भ्रंश् 4. कस् 5. पत् 6. पद् and 7. स्कन्द्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८५|नुगतोऽनुनासिकान्तस्य|नुगतोऽनुनासिकान्तस्य ७.४.८५|७.४.८५ नुगतोऽनुनासिकान्तस्य
The augment नुक् (न्) is added after the short अ of a reduplicate in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्) when the root ends in a nasal.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८६|जपजभदहदशभञ्जपशां च|जपजभदहदशभञ्जपशां च ७.४.८६|७.४.८६ जपजभदहदशभञ्जपशां च
The augment नुक् (न्) comes after the reduplicates of 1. जप 2. जभ 3. दह 4. दश 5. भञ्ज and 6. पश in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८७|चरफलोश्च|चरफलोश्च ७.४.८७|७.४.८७ चरफलोश्च
The augment नुक् (न्) comes after the reduplicates of चर् and फल् in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८८|उत्‌ परस्यातः|उत्‌ परस्यातः ७.४.८८|७.४.८८ उत्‌ परस्यातः
For the subsequent अ (i.e. for the अ of the root and not of the reduplicate), there is substituted उ in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.८९|ति च|ति च ७.४.८९|७.४.८९ ति च
उ is substituted for the vowel of चर् and फल् before an affix beginning with त्।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.९०|रीगृदुपधस्य च|रीगृदुपधस्य च ७.४.९०|७.४.९० रीगृदुपधस्य च
The reduplicate of a root which has ऋ at the penultimate position, gets the augment री in the Intensive (with expressed or elided यङ्).<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.९१|रुग्रिकौ च लुकि|रुग्रिकौ च लुकि ७.४.९१|७.४.९१ रुग्रिकौ च लुकि
The augments come after the reduplicate of a root which has ऋ at the penultimate position, only when the यङ् of the Intensive is elided.<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.९२|ऋतश्च|ऋतश्च ७.४.९२|७.४.९२ ऋतश्च
The reduplicate of a root which ends in short ऋ gets, in the Intensive without यङ् the above augments (1. रीक् 2. रुक् and 3. रिक्), 1. रि 2. र् and 3. रि।<br><br>Terms: Reduplicate

७.४.९३|सन्वल्लघुनि चङ्परेऽनग्लोपे|सन्वल्लघुनि चङ्परेऽनग्लोपे ७.४.९३|७.४.९३ सन्वल्लघुनि चङ्परेऽनग्लोपे
