८.३.९८|सुषामादिषु च|सुषामादिषु च ८.३.९८|८.३.९८ सुषामादिषु च
ष् is substituted for the स् of the words सुषामान् etc.<br><br>Terms: ष change

८.३.९९|ऐति संज्ञायामगात्‌|ऐति संज्ञायामगात्‌ ८.३.९९|८.३.९९ ऐति संज्ञायामगात्‌
ष् is substituted for the स् when followed by ए and preceded by इण् or कु , when the word is a name and when the स् is not preceded by ग्।<br><br>Terms: षत्व change

