८.४.३|पूर्वपदात्‌ संज्ञायामगः|पूर्वपदात्‌ संज्ञायामगः ८.४.३|८.४.३ पूर्वपदात्‌ संज्ञायामगः
So also, न् is replaced by ण् , when the letter occasioning the substitution, occurs in the first member of a compound, and the whole compound is a Name, provided that the first member does not end with the letter ग।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

