८.४.५|प्रनिरन्तःशरेक्षुप्लक्षाम्रकार्ष्यखदिरपियूक्षाभ्योऽसंज्ञायामपि|प्रनिरन्तःशरेक्षुप्लक्षाम्रकार्ष्यखदिरपियूक्षाभ्योऽसंज्ञायामपि ८.४.५|८.४.५ प्रनिरन्तःशरेक्षुप्लक्षाम्रकार्ष्यखदिरपियूक्षाभ्योऽसंज्ञायामपि
The न of वन , is replaced by ण , even when the compound is not a Name, when it is preceded by the words प्र , निर् , अन्तर , शर , इक्षु , प्लक्ष , आम्र , कार्ष्य , खदिर and पीयूक्षा।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

८.४.६|विभाषौषधिवनस्पतिभ्यः|विभाषौषधिवनस्पतिभ्यः ८.४.६|८.४.६ विभाषौषधिवनस्पतिभ्यः
The न of वन , is optionally replaced by ण , when the cause of change occurs in the first member of the compound and which denotes a perrenial herb or forest tree.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

८.४.७|अह्नोऽदन्तात्‌|अह्नोऽदन्तात्‌ ८.४.७|८.४.७ अह्नोऽदन्तात्‌
The ण is the substitute of न of अहन् , when it is preceded by a word ending in अ , having in it a letter capable of producing a change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास

८.४.८|वाहनमाहितात्‌|वाहनमाहितात्‌ ८.४.८|८.४.८ वाहनमाहितात्‌
The न of वाहन is changed into ण , when the letter producing the change, occurs in the first member of a compound, denoting the thing carried.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word

८.४.९|पानं देशे|पानं देशे ८.४.९|८.४.९ पानं देशे
The न of पान is changed into ण , when occurs as the second member of a compound, the first member of which contains a letter causing change; and the whole compound denotes a country or people.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास-word

८.४.१०|वा भावकरणयोः|वा भावकरणयोः ८.४.१०|८.४.१० वा भावकरणयोः
Optionally when the compound denotes a condition or an instrument, the न् of पान is changed to ण , when it is a second member, the cause of change occurring in the first member in a compound.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास-word

८.४.११|प्रातिपदिकान्तनुम्विभक्तिषु च|प्रातिपदिकान्तनुम्विभक्तिषु च ८.४.११|८.४.११ प्रातिपदिकान्तनुम्विभक्तिषु च
Optionally ण is substituted for न when it stands at the end of a Nominal-stem (प्रातिपदिक) or is the augment नुम् or is न of a case-affix, (when the cause of change occurs in the first member of the compound).<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-समास-word

८.४.१२|एकाजुत्तरपदे णः|एकाजुत्तरपदे णः ८.४.१२|८.४.१२ एकाजुत्तरपदे णः
In a compound, the second member of which is a monosyllable, there is ण in the room of न of the second member, provided that the न is at the end of a प्रातिपदिक , or is the augment नुम् , or occurs in a विभक्ति; and when the first member contains a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-आगमन-विभक्ति

८.४.१३|कुमति च|कुमति च ८.४.१३|८.४.१३ कुमति च
In a compound, the second member of which contains a guttural, there is ण in the room of न , that follows anything which standing in the prior member is qualified to cause the change, provided the न be at the end of a प्रातिपदिक , or be the augment नुम् , or occur in a विभक्ति।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-आगमन-विभक्ति

८.४.१४|उपसर्गादसमासेऽपि णोपदेशस्य|उपसर्गादसमासेऽपि णोपदेशस्य ८.४.१४|८.४.१४ उपसर्गादसमासेऽपि णोपदेशस्य
Of a root which has ण in its original enunciation, when it comes after a cause of such change standing in an उपसर्ग , even though the word be not a समास , the न is changed to ण।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-आगमन-विभक्ति

८.४.१५|हिनुमीना|हिनुमीना ८.४.१५|८.४.१५ हिनुमीना
The न of हिनु and मीना is changed to ण , when coming after an उपसर्ग containing in it a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु-उपसर्ग

८.४.१६|आनि लोट्|आनि लोट् ८.४.१६|८.४.१६ आनि लोट्
The न of आनि , the affix of the Imperative, First Person, is changed into ण when it follows a letter competent to cause such a change standing in an उपसर्ग।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word-उपसर्ग

८.४.१७|नेर्गदनदपतपदघुमास्यतिहन्तियातिवातिद्रातिप्सातिवपतिवहतिशाम्यतिचिनोतिदेग्धिषु च|नेर्गदनदपतपदघुमास्यतिहन्तियातिवातिद्रातिप्सातिवपतिवहतिशाम्यतिचिनोतिदेग्धिषु च ८.४.१७|८.४.१७ नेर्गदनदपतपदघुमास्यतिहन्तियातिवातिद्रातिप्सातिवपतिवहतिशाम्यतिचिनोतिदेग्धिषु च
The ण is the substitute of न् of the prefix नि , following a cause for such change standing in an उपसर्ग when these words follow - गद 'to speak', नद 'to be happy', पत 'to fall', पद 'to go'; the घु verbs - मा 'to measure', शो 'to destroy', हन् 'to kill', या 'to go', वा 'to blow', द्रा 'to flee', प्शा 'to eat', वप् 'to weave', वह् 'to bear', शम् 'to be tranquil', चि 'to collect', and दिह् 'to anoint'.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-तिङ्-उपसर्ग

८.४.१८|शेषे विभाषाऽकखादावषान्त उपदेशे|शेषे विभाषाऽकखादावषान्त उपदेशे ८.४.१८|८.४.१८ शेषे विभाषाऽकखादावषान्त उपदेशे
In the remaining verbs, optionally the न of नि is replaced by ण , when it is preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to cause the change; provided that, in the original enunciation, the verb has not an initial क or ख , nor ends with ष।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु-उपसर्ग

८.४.१९|अनितेः|अनितेः ८.४.१९|८.४.१९ अनितेः
The न of the verb अन् 'to breathe', is changed to ण , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to produce the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२०|अन्तः|अन्तः ८.४.२०|८.४.२० अन्तः
The न of the verb अन् 'to breathe', is changed to ण , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to produce the change, provided it occurs at the end of a पद।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२१|उभौ साभ्यासस्य|उभौ साभ्यासस्य ८.४.२१|८.४.२१ उभौ साभ्यासस्य
Both the न-s are changed into ण in the reduplicated forms of the verb अन् , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to cause the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२२|हन्तेरत्पूर्वस्य|हन्तेरत्पूर्वस्य ८.४.२२|८.४.२२ हन्तेरत्पूर्वस्य
The न , when preceded by अ , in the root हन् , is changed to ण , when the verb is preceded by a preposition competent to cause the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२३|वमोर्वा|वमोर्वा ८.४.२३|८.४.२३ वमोर्वा
Optionally when व or म follow, the न of हन् is changed to ण , when preceded by an उपसर्ग competent to cause the change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२४|अन्तरदेशे|अन्तरदेशे ८.४.२४|८.४.२४ अन्तरदेशे
The न preceded by short अ of the root हन् is changed into ण , when the root follows the उपसर्ग - अन्तर and the word does not mean 'a country'.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२५|अयनं च|अयनं च ८.४.२५|८.४.२५ अयनं च
The न of अयन is changed to ण , when preceded by the word अन्तर् and the word does not denote a country.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२६|छन्दस्यृदवग्रहात्‌|छन्दस्यृदवग्रहात्‌ ८.४.२६|८.४.२६ छन्दस्यृदवग्रहात्‌
In the छन्दस् , न of a second term is changed into ण , when prior term ends with a short ऋ even when there is an अवग्रह or hiatus between the two terms.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु

८.४.२७|नश्च धातुस्थोरुषुभ्यः|नश्च धातुस्थोरुषुभ्यः ८.४.२७|८.४.२७ नश्च धातुस्थोरुषुभ्यः
In the छन्दस् , the न of (the Pronoun) नस् is changed into ण , when it comes after a root having a र or ष or after the words उरु and षु (सु)।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-छन्दस्

८.४.२८|उपसर्गाद् बहुलम्|उपसर्गाद् बहुलम् ८.४.२८|८.४.२८ उपसर्गाद् बहुलम्
The न of नस् is changed diversely into ण , when it comes after an उपसर्ग having a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-छन्दस्

८.४.२९|कृत्यचः|कृत्यचः ८.४.२९|८.४.२९ कृत्यचः
The न of कृत् affix, preceded by a vowel, is changed into ण , when it follows an उपसर्ग having the cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word-उपसर्ग

८.४.३०|णेर्विभाषा|णेर्विभाषा ८.४.३०|८.४.३० णेर्विभाषा
The न of कृत् affix ordained after a causative verb (णयन्त), is optionally changed into ण , when it comes after an उपसर्ग having a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

८.४.३१|हलश्च इजुपधात्‌|हलश्च इजुपधात्‌ ८.४.३१|८.४.३१ हलश्च इजुपधात्‌
The कृत् affix, coming after a verb, which begins with a consonant and has a penultimate इच् vowel, changes optionally its न् , which is preceded by a vowel, into ण् , when it comes after उपसर्ग having a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

८.४.३२|इजादेः सनुमः|इजादेः सनुमः ८.४.३२|८.४.३२ इजादेः सनुमः
A कृत् affix ordained after a verb beginning with an इच् vowel, having the augment नुम् in it, and ending with a consonant, changes it s न् into ण् , when preceded by an उपसर्ग having in it the cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

८.४.३३|वा निंसनिक्षनिन्दाम्|वा निंसनिक्षनिन्दाम् ८.४.३३|८.४.३३ वा निंसनिक्षनिन्दाम्
The न् of निस् , निक्ष and निन्द is changed to a ण optionally, when preceded by an उपसर्ग having in it a cause of change.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-कृत्-उपसर्ग

८.४.३४|न भाभूपूकमिगमिप्यायीवेपाम्|न भाभूपूकमिगमिप्यायीवेपाम् ८.४.३४|८.४.३४ न भाभूपूकमिगमिप्यायीवेपाम्
The न of a कृत् affix is not changed to ण , though preceded by an उपसर्ग having in it a cause of change, when the affix is added to the following verbs - भा 'to shine', भू 'to be', पू 'to purify', कमि 'to be brilliant', गमि 'to go', प्यायि 'to increase', वेप 'to shake'.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word-उपसर्ग

८.४.३५|षात्‌ पदान्तात्‌|षात्‌ पदान्तात्‌ ८.४.३५|८.४.३५ षात्‌ पदान्तात्‌
After a ष् final in a पद , the न् is not changed to ण।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-धातु-उपसर्ग

८.४.३६|नशेः षान्तस्य|नशेः षान्तस्य ८.४.३६|८.४.३६ नशेः षान्तस्य
ण् is not the substitute of the verb नश 'to destroy', when ending in ष्।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.३७|पदान्तस्य|पदान्तस्य ८.४.३७|८.४.३७ पदान्तस्य
Of a न् final in a पद , ण् is not the substitute.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.३८|पदव्यवायेऽपि|पदव्यवायेऽपि ८.४.३८|८.४.३८ पदव्यवायेऽपि
The न् is not changed to ण् when a पद intervenes between the cause of the change and the word containing the न्।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.३९|क्षुभ्नाऽऽदिषु च|क्षुभ्नाऽऽदिषु च ८.४.३९|८.४.३९ क्षुभ्नाऽऽदिषु च
The ण् is not the susbtitute of न् in the words क्षुभ्ना etc.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४०|स्तोः श्चुना श्चुः|स्तोः श्चुना श्चुः ८.४.४०|८.४.४० स्तोः श्चुना श्चुः
The letters स् and the dentals when coming in contact with श् and the palatals, are changed to श् and palatals respectively.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्-word

८.४.४१|ष्टुना ष्टुः|ष्टुना ष्टुः ८.४.४१|८.४.४१ ष्टुना ष्टुः
The letters स् and the dentals when coming in contact with ष् and the cerebrals, are changed to ष् and cerebrals respectively.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४२|न पदान्ताट्टोरनाम्|न पदान्ताट्टोरनाम् ८.४.४२|८.४.४२ न पदान्ताट्टोरनाम्
After टु final in a पद , the change of a dental (स्तु) to a cerebral (ष्टु), does not take place, except in the case of the affix नाम्।<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४३|तोः षि|तोः षि ८.४.४३|८.४.४३ तोः षि
In the room of तु there is not a cerebral substitute, when ष् follows.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४४|शात्‌|शात्‌ ८.४.४४|८.४.४४ शात्‌
In the room of तु there is not a palatal substitute, when श् precedes.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४५|यरोऽनुनासिकेऽनुनासिको वा|यरोऽनुनासिकेऽनुनासिको वा ८.४.४५|८.४.४५ यरोऽनुनासिकेऽनुनासिको वा
In the room of a यर् letter (every consonant except ह final) in a पद , when Nasal follows, there is optionally a Nasal substitute.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४६|अचो रहाभ्यां द्वे|अचो रहाभ्यां द्वे ८.४.४६|८.४.४६ अचो रहाभ्यां द्वे
There is reduplication of यर् , i.e. all the consonants except ह after the letters र् and ह् following a vowel.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४७|अनचि च|अनचि च ८.४.४७|८.४.४७ अनचि च
When a vowel does not follow, there is reduplication of यर् (all consonants except ह) after a vowel.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४८|नादिन्याक्रोशे पुत्रस्य|नादिन्याक्रोशे पुत्रस्य ८.४.४८|८.४.४८ नादिन्याक्रोशे पुत्रस्य
There is not reduplication of the letters of पुत्र , when the word आदिनी follows, the sense being that of reviling or cursing.<br><br>Terms: सन्धि-हल्

८.४.४९|शरोऽचि|शरोऽचि ८.४.४९|८.४.४९ शरोऽचि
There are not two in the room of a sibilant (शर्), when a vowel follows.<br><br>Terms: 

८.४.५०|त्रिप्रभृतिषु शाकटायनस्य|त्रिप्रभृतिषु शाकटायनस्य ८.४.५०|८.४.५० त्रिप्रभृतिषु शाकटायनस्य
According to the option of शाकटायन , the doubling does not take place when the conjunct consonants are three or more in number.<br><br>Terms: 

८.४.५१|सर्वत्र शाकल्यस्य|सर्वत्र शाकल्यस्य ८.४.५१|८.४.५१ सर्वत्र शाकल्यस्य
According to the opnion of शाकल्य , there is reduplication no where.<br><br>Terms: 

८.४.५२|दीर्घादाचार्याणाम्|दीर्घादाचार्याणाम् ८.४.५२|८.४.५२ दीर्घादाचार्याणाम्
According to the opinion of all the Teachers, there is no doubling after a long vowel.<br><br>Terms: 

८.४.५३|झलां जश् झशि|झलां जश् झशि ८.४.५३|८.४.५३ झलां जश् झशि
In the room of झल् letters, there is substitution of जश् letters, when झश् letters follow.<br><br>Terms: 

८.४.५४|अभ्यासे चर्च्च|अभ्यासे चर्च्च ८.४.५४|८.४.५४ अभ्यासे चर्च्च
The चर् is also substitute of झल् letters occuring in a reduplicate syllable, as well as जश्।<br><br>Terms: 

८.४.५५|खरि च|खरि च ८.४.५५|८.४.५५ खरि च
In the room of झल् , there is the substitute चर् , when खर् follows.<br><br>Terms: 

